            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am very proud to be a student of GSSGS. It has a very comfortable n homely atmosphere. I have been\nstudying here for more than 10 years. This school is a total combination of proper amount of discipline, fun and learning. It gives equal opportunities to each and every kid whether it be a debate competition, dance or singing. Provides equal care to all.Teachers are the best and gives importance to every child. All in one, it is one of the best schools in every aspect.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
