          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "To be very honest G.S.S has given me the best years of my life. This place is not just a school but a second home for students. The teachers over here are so motherly and literally the best at their profession. They always tries to bring out the best in us. Even the non teaching staffs are so kind to us and takes every little initiative so that we all are not uncomfortable by any means. As per my belief I am getting the best education over here not only academically but also morally. We are surrounded by certain interesting co-curricular activities as well which refreshes us every moment .I am really very proud to be a part of this organisation.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
